a.title: Table Default.`belu_document` Documents of all projects. Every Document belongs to one project, which has a owner, who is implicit the owner of the documents. The document can be approved to a betareader for korrection.
Table Default.`belu_betareader` Table of all betareaders and their bind attributes

Referred by `belu_beta_genre` ( `BetaID` ) Referred by `belu_beta_job` ( `BetaID` ) Referred by `belu_beta_project` ( `BetaID` ) Referred by `belu_beta_textsort` ( `BetaID` ) Referred by `belu_beta_theme` ( `BetaID` ) Referred by belu_beta_language_focus ( betaid -> `BetaID` ) Referred by belu_beta_dialect ( betaid -> `BetaID` ) Referred by belu_beta_facts ( betaid -> `BetaID` ) Referred by belu_beta_facts ( betaid -> `BetaID` ) Referred by belu_beta_language ( betaid -> `BetaID` ) Referred by belu_beta_language ( betaid -> `BetaID` )
`Capacity` int Maximal number of projects, this betareader reads for
Table Default.`belu_beta_project` Link betareader with projects
Table Default.`belu_beta_theme` Table of themepreferences of betareader
`Priority` int Preference of betareader for theme
`themereference` int Reference to a other theme via ID (eg. ID of ''Fantasy'' for ''Dark Fantasy'')
Table Default.`belu_genre` List of valid genres for projects
Table Default.`belu_beta_genre` List of genres for a betareader
`GenrePriority` int Preference of betareader for genre
Table Default.`belu_project_theme` Link projects with one or many themes
Referred by `belu_betareader` ( `UserID` ) Referred by `belu_project` ( `UserID` ) Referred by `belu_user_absence` ( `UserID` ) Referred by belu_facts ( proposeduser -> `UserID` )
`AgeDisplay` * enum default 'N' Show Age of User in profile in Years (20 Y), Range (20-30 Y) or not
`EmailDisplay` * enum default 'N' Show Email (Y) or not in profile (N)
Table Default.`belu_beta_job` Table of betajobs on ducumentlevel with their status.
`StartDate` date The day the job gets "In Progress"
`EndDate` date The day the betareader set the status on Ready
`deadline` date The day the projectowner wants the betareader to finish the job
Table Default.`belu_beta_textsort` Table of textsortpreferences of betareader
Table Default.`belu_project` Table of writingprojects from users
Referred by `belu_document` ( `ProjectID` ) Referred by `belu_project_theme` ( `ProjektID` -> `ProjectID` ) Referred by belu_project_betasearch ( projectid -> `ProjectID` )
`UserID` * int ID of the owner the project
Table Default.`belu_textsort` List of valid sorts of texts
